<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome to the Bitshala Fellowship</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#111111; font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;">

  <div style="display:none; max-height:0; overflow:hidden; mso-hide:all; visibility:hidden; opacity:0; color:transparent;">
    Your Bitshala Fellowship workspace, contract, and next steps are inside.
    &#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;&#8199;
  </div>

  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#111111; padding:24px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">

        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#1b1b1b; border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden;">

          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="background-color:#000000; padding:24px 24px 20px 24px;">
              <h1 style="margin:0; font-size:24px; color:#ffffff; font-weight:700;">
                Welcome <%~ it.userName %>!
              </h1>
              <p style="margin:8px 0 0 0; font-size:14px; color:#f9b233; font-weight:500;">
                Your <%~ it.fellowshipType %> Fellowship Application Has Been Accepted
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:24px 32px 8px 32px; color:#eaeaea; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">Dear <%~ it.userName %>,</p>
              <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">
                We are thrilled to inform you that you have been selected for the
                <strong style="color:#f9b233;">Bitshala <%~ it.fellowshipType %> Fellowship</strong>!
                We're excited to see your impact and contributions and look forward to
                working with you over the months ahead.
              </p>
              <p style="margin:0;">
                We've set up a
                <a href="<%~ it.driveFolderUrl %>" style="color:#f9b233; text-decoration:underline;">Google Drive folder</a>
                where your contracts and tax forms will be collected. Your monthly
                work reports are submitted through the
                <a href="https://app.bitshala.org/" style="color:#f9b233; text-decoration:underline;">Bitshala app</a>.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:24px 32px 0 32px;">
              <div style="height:1px; background-color:#2e2e2e; line-height:1px; font-size:1px;">&nbsp;</div>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:20px 32px 8px 32px;">
              <h2 style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:18px; color:#ffd580;">Next Steps</h2>

              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-bottom:12px; background-color:#262626; border-radius:12px;">
                <tr>
                  <td width="48" valign="top" style="padding:16px 0 16px 16px;">
                    <div style="width:32px; height:32px; line-height:32px; text-align:center; border-radius:999px; background-color:#f7931a; color:#000000; font-weight:700; font-size:14px;">1</div>
                  </td>
                  <td style="padding:16px 16px 16px 12px; color:#eaeaea; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6;">
                    <strong style="color:#ffffff;">Sign the Contract.</strong>
                    Your contract — already signed by Bitshala — is in the Drive
                    folder. Add your signature and upload the signed copy back to
                    the same folder. Make sure the contract date matches the date
                    in the contract document.
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-bottom:12px; background-color:#262626; border-radius:12px;">
                <tr>
                  <td width="48" valign="top" style="padding:16px 0 16px 16px;">
                    <div style="width:32px; height:32px; line-height:32px; text-align:center; border-radius:999px; background-color:#f7931a; color:#000000; font-weight:700; font-size:14px;">2</div>
                  </td>
                  <td style="padding:16px 16px 16px 12px; color:#eaeaea; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6;">
                    <strong style="color:#ffffff;">Submit Your W-8BEN Form.</strong>
                    We require a completed W-8BEN form for U.S. tax compliance on
                    monthly payouts. Download the form from
                    <a href="https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-pdf/fw8ben.pdf" style="color:#f9b233; text-decoration:underline;">irs.gov</a>,
                    fill it out (India-specific guidance below), and upload the
                    completed form to the Drive folder.
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-bottom:12px; background-color:#262626; border-radius:12px;">
                <tr>
                  <td width="48" valign="top" style="padding:16px 0 16px 16px;">
                    <div style="width:32px; height:32px; line-height:32px; text-align:center; border-radius:999px; background-color:#f7931a; color:#000000; font-weight:700; font-size:14px;">3</div>
                  </td>
                  <td style="padding:16px 16px 16px 12px; color:#eaeaea; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6;">
                    <strong style="color:#ffffff;">Share Account Details.</strong>
                    Monthly payments are processed through <strong>Skydo</strong>.
                    You'll receive a separate email from Skydo with a form for your
                    account and contact info — please fill it in.
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#262626; border-radius:12px;">
                <tr>
                  <td width="48" valign="top" style="padding:16px 0 16px 16px;">
                    <div style="width:32px; height:32px; line-height:32px; text-align:center; border-radius:999px; background-color:#f7931a; color:#000000; font-weight:700; font-size:14px;">4</div>
                  </td>
                  <td style="padding:16px 16px 16px 12px; color:#eaeaea; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6;">
                    <strong style="color:#ffffff;">Complete Onboarding.</strong>
                    Once the above is done, log in to
                    <a href="https://app.bitshala.org/" style="color:#f9b233; text-decoration:underline;">app.bitshala.org</a>
                    and finish the fellowship onboarding form (mentor contact, project
                    details, GitHub profile).
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:24px 32px 0 32px;">
              <div style="height:1px; background-color:#2e2e2e; line-height:1px; font-size:1px;">&nbsp;</div>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:20px 32px 4px 32px;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 4px 0; font-size:11px; color:#888888; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.6px;">Reference</p>
              <h3 style="margin:0 0 4px 0; font-size:14px; color:#cfcfcf;">W-8BEN Form — India-Specific Guidance</h3>
              <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:11px; color:#888888; line-height:1.5;">
                Use this if you're filing from India. Skip if it doesn't apply.
                Form:
                <a href="https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-pdf/fw8ben.pdf" style="color:#888888; text-decoration:underline;">irs.gov/pub/irs-pdf/fw8ben.pdf</a>
              </p>

              <p style="margin:8px 0 2px 0; font-size:11px; color:#aaaaaa; font-weight:600;">
                Part I — Identification of Beneficial Owner
              </p>
              <ul style="padding-left:18px; margin:0 0 10px 0; color:#888888; font-size:11px; line-height:1.6;">
                <li><strong style="color:#aaaaaa;">1:</strong> Your full name</li>
                <li><strong style="color:#aaaaaa;">2:</strong> Your country of citizenship</li>
                <li><strong style="color:#aaaaaa;">3:</strong> Full street address — city, state/province, postal code, country</li>
                <li><strong style="color:#aaaaaa;">4:</strong> Optional, only if mailing address differs from line 3</li>
                <li><strong style="color:#aaaaaa;">5:</strong> Leave blank (unless you have a U.S. tax ID)</li>
                <li><strong style="color:#aaaaaa;">6a:</strong> Your PAN card or relevant tax ID</li>
                <li><strong style="color:#aaaaaa;">6b:</strong> Leave blank</li>
                <li><strong style="color:#aaaaaa;">7:</strong> Date of birth (MM-DD-YYYY)</li>
              </ul>

              <p style="margin:8px 0 2px 0; font-size:11px; color:#aaaaaa; font-weight:600;">
                Part II — Claim of Tax Treaty Benefits
              </p>
              <ul style="padding-left:18px; margin:0 0 10px 0; color:#888888; font-size:11px; line-height:1.6;">
                <li><strong style="color:#aaaaaa;">9a:</strong> India</li>
                <li><strong style="color:#aaaaaa;">10:</strong> Article <strong>15 (Independent Personal Services)</strong> of the treaty on line 9 — claims a <strong>0% withholding rate</strong>.</li>
                <li><strong style="color:#aaaaaa;">Additional conditions:</strong> "Beneficial owner has a permanent establishment only in India and all work is done in India as per Article 5 (Permanent Establishment)."</li>
              </ul>

              <p style="margin:8px 0 2px 0; font-size:11px; color:#aaaaaa; font-weight:600;">
                Part III — Certification
              </p>
              <ul style="padding-left:18px; margin:0; color:#888888; font-size:11px; line-height:1.6;">
                <li>Sign, date, and complete the form.</li>
              </ul>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:24px 32px 0 32px;">
              <div style="height:1px; background-color:#2e2e2e; line-height:1px; font-size:1px;">&nbsp;</div>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding:24px 32px 8px 32px; color:#eaeaea; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;">Ready to get started? Open your fellowship workspace below.</p>
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" bgcolor="#f7931a" style="border-radius:999px;">
                    <a href="<%~ it.driveFolderUrl %>"
                       style="display:inline-block; padding:14px 32px; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#000000; text-decoration:none;">
                      Open Fellowship Drive Folder
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:16px 32px 32px 32px; color:#eaeaea; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">
                If you have any questions or need clarification, email us at
                <a href="mailto:fellowship@bitshala.org" style="color:#f9b233; text-decoration:underline;">fellowship@bitshala.org</a>
                — we're here to support you every step of the way.
              </p>
              <p style="margin:0;">Welcome aboard, and we look forward to achieving great things together!</p>
              <p style="margin:16px 0 0 0; color:#9a9a9a;">— Team Bitshala</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>

      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
